==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: epidemiology
<hw>ep`i*de`mi*ol"o*gy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Epidemy</ets> + <ets>-logy</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>That branch of medicine which studies the incidence and
distribution of disease in a population, and uses such information to
find the causes, modes of transmission, and methods for control of
disease.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Epidemy</ent>⟦br⟧
